#################
Status Changes
#################
Poison - HP loss every turn
Curse - HP loss every attack -OR- does not attack
Darkness - AGI decrease for attacks and defense
Slow - AGI decrease for turn frequency
Stop - misses 1 or more turns
Haste - AGI increase for turn frequency
Confused - Attack oneself or not attack at all (funny messages)
Asleep - Can't move.  Perhaps awakened by being attacked?
Petrify - Can't move and don't wake up.  can still be attacked.
Mute - Cannot cast spells
Invisible - Do not attract enemies
